# ===== .NET Backend =====

# Build output
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/

# NuGet
**/packages/
**/.nuget/

# IDE / Editor
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.rider/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Logs & temp
**/logs/
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp
*.swp

# OS files
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
desktop.ini

# Database backups
*.backup
*.bak
*.sql

# Backup folders
backup/

# Images/media (binary)
Images/

# PowerShell reports (utility scripts)
test_*.ps1
check_*.ps1

# EF Core migrations snapshots (large auto-generated)
**/Migrations/*.Designer.cs
**/Migrations/*ModelSnapshot.cs

# ===== Vue 3 / TypeScript Frontend =====

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/

# Build output
**/dist/
**/.output/
**/.nuxt/

# Cache
**/.cache/
**/.parcel-cache/
**/.vite/

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# TypeScript build info
*.tsbuildinfo

# Coverage
**/coverage/

# Lock files (large, not needed for code understanding)
**/yarn.lock
**/package-lock.json
**/pnpm-lock.yaml

# ===== Git worktrees =====
.claude/worktrees/

